                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ep-a_text" data-visibility750="false" data-visibility640="false" data-visibility480="false" data-visibility320="false">
                <p>The EU has approved emergency measures to help farmers and fishermen affected by the coronavirus pandemic. </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>


            

                

